videos.description: Penn State gets out in transition and it leads to Josh Reaves' 3-pointer to extend Penn State's lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Reaves drains transition 3-pointer

videos.description: Wisconsin forward Khalil Iverson fires a pass to Ethan Happ, who finishes with the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Happ finishes slam

videos.description: Penn State's Lamar Stevens skies for the emphatic block on Wisconsin's Nate Reuvers.
videos.headline: Stevens says NO to Reuvers
